treatments.description:
As you stretch out on our amber and quartz bed, this soothing massage (medium to deep pressure) uses a silky body balm enriched with powerful succinic acid &mdash; aimed to nourish and relax you while easing muscle tension through classic massage techniques and pssamotherapy.<br />
<br />
&nbsp;

Our warm and relaxing treatment stimulates your cells as you lie on a specialized bed blanketed in gorgeous quartz sand. In conjunction with massage oil, our spin on hot sand therapy aims to relieve tension and stress, making you feel like the kings and queens of self-care.<br />
<br />
&nbsp;

Enhanced by the use of aroma oils, our customizable Swedish-style massage focuses on relieving tension, stimulating blood circulation and overall relaxation. You can choose from 50, 75, or 100 minutes.<br />
<br />
&nbsp;
